        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 9–12. Malenka diablo sp. n., Colorado Creek, Santa Clara County, California. Epiproct dorsal sclerite (A: yellow); paraproct, median lobe (C: green); mesobasal lobe of cercus (D: purple); vesicle (E: orange); hypoproct (F: turquoise). 9. Right cercus and mesobasal lobe, dorsal. 10. Right cercus and mesobasal lobe, lateral. 11. Terminalia (vesicle and hypoproct), ventral. 12. Female sterna 7–10, ventral." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4758033/files/figure.png" .

